#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.253:0.2"
msgid "26. Upasampadāvagga "
msgstr "26. Ordination "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an5.253:0.3"
msgid "253. Sāmaṇerasutta "
msgstr "253. Who Should Have a Novice as Attendant "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an5.253:1.1"
msgid "“Pañcahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgatena bhikkhunā sāmaṇero upaṭṭhāpetabbo. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, a novice should attend on a mendicant with five qualities. "

msgctxt "an5.253:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi pañcahi? "
msgstr "What five? "

msgctxt "an5.253:1.3"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu asekhena sīlakkhandhena samannāgato hoti; asekhena samādhikkhandhena … asekhena paññākkhandhena … asekhena vimuttikkhandhena … asekhena vimuttiñāṇadassanakkhandhena samannāgato hoti. "
msgstr "It’s a mendicant who has the entire spectrum of an adept’s ethics, immersion, wisdom, freedom, and the knowledge and vision of freedom. "

msgctxt "an5.253:1.4"
msgid "Imehi kho, bhikkhave, pañcahi dhammehi samannāgatena bhikkhunā sāmaṇero upaṭṭhāpetabbo”ti. "
msgstr "A novice should attend on a mendicant with these five qualities.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.253:1.5"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

